Honda attacks for second time with its bestseller
In November, Honda will begin the sale of the second-generation Jazz.
If the predecessor of this single-space vehicle already has considerable space, it now offers an even more spacious interior.
This is joined by improved engines that increase driving comfort and allow for greater fuel efficiency.
